Text: "\U0001F493\U0001F49D ~~*my review ofNelliyampathy It's a new experience~*~\
  \ \U0001F60D\U0001F496\n\n\n                                    We have designed\
  \ a 2-day immersive experience.We'll find time to play, to make and to do, we'll\
  \ explore our relationship with wildness and how it can be used to fuel our collective\
  \ creativity.We'll eat great local food around a fire, camp under the stars and\
  \ watch the forest come alive in the morning.We'll do exercises designed to challenge\
  \ ourselves and learn new things about ourselves and the way we work together.\n\
  Our Camp Lead N.A. Naseer sir ( wildlife photographer)gave us the Basic Class of\
  \ Photography and the ''greenwalkers\" team head  Manuoop (wildlife photographer)and\
  \ Family.with our video and photos anjulal and all the members are creating a new\
  \ world all.Wandering through thick lush forests fill me up with something so unlike\
  \ anything else.\nI\u2019m trying to take some photos and videos that can maybe\
  \ share a little bit of that feeling with you all.I\u2019m gathering inspiration\
  \ for some work to do in January.I can\u2019t wait to show  .\nCamping out with\
  \ friends is amazing - I don\u2019t do it enough actually, but there\u2019s also\
  \ something magical about being out alone.\n love it!the new camp and the new places\
  \ to restore their power and health..\U0001F60C\n                   By\n       \
  \                anvarsadath.k"
